    • Method Detail

      • run

        public void run()
        Runs the PO algorithm and writes audit information to the audit file and displays the results and winner information of the eleciton to the screen. Assumes the electionFile Scanner object begins on the second line, all information contained in the CPL election ballot file is entered properly, there is at least one ballot in the file and at least one candidate. Takes no parameters and returns nothing. Generates an audit file. Assumes election class has been initialized properly
        Overrides:
        run in class Election
